        <Parent_String>bonds (masonry technique) [300175495], surface covering processes and techniques [300229469], additive and joining processes and techniques [300229467], processes and techniques by specific type [300053003], Processes and Techniques (hierarchy name) [300053001], Activities Facet [300264090]</Parent_String>
